Hedgie Thunder: Loud thundering makes Pins and Nettie anxious. But once they think of the thunder as wild rather than scary, they then realise that thunderstorms can actually be quite fun.
It's Time for a Harvest Festival: JoJo and Gran Gran join Julie at the farm for the harvest festival.
It's Time to Make a Family Tree: Great-Gran Gran shows JoJo an old family photo - it's fun spotting Gran Gran, Mummy and Great-Gran Gran when they were younger.
When the fairies accidentally land their ball in a thorny bush, Doireann the spider is happy to weave a clever solution, teaching them to appreciate her hard work and creativity.
The friends learn how composting helps gardens grow, but when Rua skips a step, they discover that patience and teamwork are key to making healthy compost.
Fun and games with the animals of the forest.

Symphony of Flavour: There's no build too big & no problem too small for these two twins.
